Class SQLServerQueryLevelTableIndexHint

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.database.SQLServerQueryLevelHintBase
      • gw.api.database.SQLServerQueryLevelTableIndexHint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryHint

    public class SQLServerQueryLevelTableIndexHint
extends SQLServerQueryLevelHintBase
    This is a Query Hint that specifies, for a given table, to use the given index. http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms181714.aspx E.g. TABLE HINT(qRoot, INDEX(ab0000004gN6))
